title: I got S- on level 5 Twitch. I should get a token right?
body: I got S- on level 5 Twitch but never got the token. Please what did I do wrong??? How do I fix this??

replies.body: Was it a match that you were already mastery level 5 in and was it also in a ranked or normal Summoner's Rift match?
Already level 5 and it was just a normal Summoner's Rift match.
